    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that redefines what it means to be 'showroom quality.' This vehicle has been maintained to the most exacting standards, preserved in a state that is indistinguishable from the day it left the factory. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, scent-free cabin, reflects a history of meticulous care and climate-controlled storage. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is an unrivaled opportunity to own the finest example of its kind.",
      "price": 49500.0,
